<!-- Settings Help --><div class="help-section"><nav class="help-breadcrumb"><a href="/help">Help</a> / <span>Settings</span></nav><h1><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> Settings</h1><p class="help-intro">Configure your NonProfit Finance application.</p><div class="help-block"><h2>Organization Settings</h2><table class="help-table"><tr><td><strong>Organization Name</strong></td><td>Your nonprofit's legal name</td></tr><tr><td><strong>EIN (Tax ID)</strong></td><td>Federal employer identification number (XX-XXXXXXX)</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Fiscal Year Start</strong></td><td>First month of your fiscal year</td></tr><tr><td><strong>State</strong></td><td>State of incorporation (for state filings)</td></tr></table></div><div class="help-block"><h2>Appearance Settings</h2><ul><li><strong>Theme</strong> - Light or Dark mode</li><li><strong>Date Format</strong> - MM/DD/YYYY or DD/MM/YYYY</li><li><strong>Currency</strong> - USD or other currency symbol</li></ul></div><div class="help-block"><h2>Compliance Settings</h2><ul><li><strong>$1M Revenue Alerts</strong> - Warn when approaching audit threshold</li><li><strong>State Filing Reminders</strong> - Tennessee Secretary of State deadlines</li><li><strong>Grant Expiration Reminders</strong> - Alert before grants expire</li><li><strong>Reminder Days</strong> - How many days before due date to alert</li></ul></div><div class="help-block"><h2>Notification Settings</h2><ul><li><strong>Email Notifications</strong> - Enable email alerts</li><li><strong>Notification Email</strong> - Where to send alerts</li><li><strong>Weekly Digest</strong> - Summary of financial activity</li></ul></div><div class="help-block"><h2>Data Management</h2><ul><li><strong>Backup Now</strong> - Create manual backup</li><li><strong>Automatic Backups</strong> - Schedule regular backups</li><li><strong>Import/Export</strong> - Move data in/out of system</li></ul></div></div>
